Navbar implementation spec
Files

navbar.html (or your layout template)

navbar.css

navbar.js

Requirements

Logo left

Center nav links

CTA right: Join Free

Sticky top with blur

Two scroll states:

top: 72px, translucent

scrolled: 60px, solid white + border + soft shadow

Nav links:

hover: text turns accent + underline animates in

active: text accent + underline stays visible

Accessibility:

keyboard focus ring

aria-current="page" for active link

skip link recommended

<!-- Optional but recommended for accessibility -->
<a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

<header class="site-header" role="banner">
